WEBVTT

00:00:00.144 --> 00:00:01.464
Kam ardhur sot ketu

00:00:01.464 --> 00:00:04.151
te flas per nje problem.

00:00:04.151 --> 00:00:07.678
Eshte njekohesisht shume i thjeshte 
dhe shkaterrues,

00:00:07.678 --> 00:00:09.623
nje problem qe shtrihet ne te gjithe globin

00:00:09.623 --> 00:00:12.536
dhe po na prek te gjitheve.

00:00:12.536 --> 00:00:14.621
Problemi eshte

00:00:14.621 --> 00:00:17.346
kompanite anonime.

00:00:17.346 --> 00:00:19.436
Tingellon si nje ceshtje e thate 
dhe shume teknike,

00:00:19.436 --> 00:00:20.492
apo jo?

00:00:20.492 --> 00:00:22.994
Por kompanite anonime 
po e bejne shume te veshtire

00:00:22.994 --> 00:00:25.546
dhe ndonjehere te pamundur

00:00:25.546 --> 00:00:27.395
te gjejne

00:00:27.395 --> 00:00:30.394
njerezit qe jane pergjegjes